data.description: Excellent location !! Brookhurst & Edinger, CORNER LOT 7,350 Square Feet, This is a Beautiful Fountain Valley Single Family home, residents can enjoy  walking distance to Shopping Plaza of Brookhurst & Edinger, Mile Square Park, Brookhurst & Heil Restaurants. The home features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing 2,006 Sq Ft of living space. The value is the corner lot home, big lot size,  3-car garage for direct access, making it an excellent choice for Families. The double door entrance leads to a living room,  family room with Fireplace and a sliding door to a huge private backyard, block walls,  nice swimming pool with fences, ideal for family gathering. The master bedroom with sliding door to the balcony. All four bedrooms are bathed in a natural light, all double pane windows.  Additionally, its convenient location places it near supermarkets, restaurants, shopping plazas, and fitness centers, making it a desirable residence in every aspect.
